name: Mechmate Token
description:
Utility: token is used to purchase Mechmate NFT, Mechmate Factory Upgrades, and more. 
Mining: token can be mined at the Mechmate Factory / +income
How to claim: Burning a Mechmate NFT or buying through secondary sales. 
Primary sale: Not Available.
Burning mechanism: When the token is used to buy any MM services it will be burned from the circulating supply.
